PURCHASING
Looking for licensing and pricing information? Read the vSphere and vSphere with Operations Management Licensing, Pricing and Packaging White Paper.

vCenter Server Standard is for large vSphere deployments.

vCenter Server Standard customers are entitled to 25 log streams of vRealize Log Insight for vCenter Server. For more information, see the FAQ.

Note that vCenter Server for any vSphere Essentials kit is already integrated into the kits for smaller office deployments.


























 
















